metadata.name: Venus Unborn
metadata.description:
A moment of waiting  
It's all that it takes  
To reach the pinnacle of my grace.

In the twirl of imagination  
Dare to touch my veins  
Seek inspiration and there will be my name.

A beauty without a face

Where I shall rise and learn my fate.

I am all art waiting to be done

Know me as Venus unborn.
